{"tid":1102582,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【與何彪拍拖5年】翁靜晶今年內再婚 電話頭像轉粉紅晚裝照","createTime":"2019-04-11T21:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T09:16:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"463a6d1eda2d86fc94b6e826ca2300f549cd010e","tid":1102582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T21:30:28.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶於19歲時嫁給比她年長30歲、黃飛鴻第四代弟子劉家良，兩人相識到育有兩名女兒，彼此情繫差不多30年，直至劉師傅於13年病逝。<br />\n今日有報道指翁靜晶與何東爵士曾孫何彪拍拖多年，兩人甚至計劃今年內再婚，翁靜晶不僅在facebook轉發該報道及寫道：「何東夫人！！」，網民紛紛送上祝福，她亦欣然接受並留言多謝大家。《蘋果》今日恭喜翁靜晶，但對於婚訊，翁靜晶說：「現開會。」不過翁靜晶的電話個人頭像就轉了相，相中她穿上粉紅晚裝及戴頭紗與一對流浪狗合影，問到是否已影婚照？她說：「這不是啦，咁醜樣。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190411/large/1554993793_0198.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190411%2Flarge%2F1554993793_0198.jpg&h=693b2a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190411/large/1554993382_a4bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190411%2Flarge%2F1554993382_a4bb.jpg&h=c8268e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190411/large/1554982878_14cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190411%2Flarge%2F1554982878_14cf.jpg&h=b85867ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190411/59476431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190411%2F59476431&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c968acd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190411%2F59476431&h=f6e98304\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190411/594764